            <div class="message-body">
              <p>There is an adventure park in Junagadh, Gujarat. It is called the Madhubhan Adventure Park and offers a variety of activities such as zip-lining, rock climbing, rappelling, rope courses, and more. The park is located on the Junagadh-Girnar Road and is open to visitors throughout the year.</p>
